This Regulation is without prejudice to the rules laid down by other Union legal acts 

regulating other aspects of the provision of services by online short-term rental platforms 

and the provision of short-term accommodation rental services, in particular: 

(a)  Regulation (EU) 2019/1150 of the European Parliament and of the Council19; 

(c)  Regulation (EU) 2022/1925 of the European Parliament and of the Council20; 

